Product Description " A must-have for the well-appointed play kitchen, these condiments sound and look like the real thing! Packaged in a handy metal caddy to keep everything organized, the six-piece set includes ketchup, mustard, salt, pepper, and hot sauce. Best of all: The salt and pepper really ""shake,"" the hot sauce really ""pours,"" and the ketchup and mustard ""squirt"" string! These wonderfully durable play pieces are built to last through countless culinary adventures. The Melissa & Doug condiments set is an exceptional learning tool for children from 3 to 5 years old. Parents and bigger kids can help smaller children identify the color of each condiment, have kids arrange the condiments by height and then ask which are tallest and which are shortest, and place the condiments in the caddy, have kids memorize where each one is, and then close their eyes. Our play condiments for kids set assists children in the development of fine motor skills and imaginative thinking and promotes pretend play. The Let’s Play House! Condiment Set is a delightful and educational gift for kids ages 3 to 5 years. Add the Melissa & Doug Breakfast Caddy Set to round out the hands-on play experience and to give kids an engaging option for screen-free fun. For more than 30 years, Melissa & Doug has created beautifully designed imagination- and creativity-sparking products that NBC News called “the gold standard in early childhood play.” We design every toy to the highest quality standards, and to nurture minds and hearts. If your child is not inspired, give us a call and we'll make it right. Our phone number is on every product! " Brand Story By Melissa & Doug P.when('A').execute(function(A) {
